item.title: Rate My Interfaces
item.dc:creator: @WowILikeToCode WowILikeToCode
item.description:
@WowILikeToCode wrote:

Lin:

The black would look better if it was lighter or had a texture. The close buttons really don’t fit in. The button outlines don’t look good with just flat white. The rest is pretty cool.

I was just playing before i made anything serious out of them, as my server is hosted i wanted your guys feedback before i released them publicly too my server, I will have a go at adding some texture too them and i wasnt really sure about the white lines myself, wasnt sure what else i could use to seperate them though.
